{"prompt": "Generate a website for a cybersecurity firm. The website should be professional and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SecureNet Solutions</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background-color: #f4f7f6;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #d32f2f; /* Brand Red */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            font-weight: 700;\n        }\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 5px;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 50px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #d32f2f; /* Brand Red */\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n        .service-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            padding: 25px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border-left: 5px solid #d32f2f; /* Brand Red accent */\n        }\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #d32f2f; /* Brand Red */\n        }\n        .service-item p {\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n            background-color: #d32f2f; /* Brand Red */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #e57373; /* Lighter Red for contrast */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #c62828; /* Darker Red on hover */\n        }\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 50px;\n        }\n        #about p {\n            line-height: 1.7;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>SecureNet Solutions</h1>\n        <p>Your Shield Against Digital Threats</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>\n                SecureNet Solutions is a leading cybersecurity firm dedicated to protecting your digital assets from evolving threats.\n                We provide comprehensive, cutting-edge security services tailored to meet the unique needs of your business.\n                Our expert team utilizes advanced strategies and technologies to ensure your data remains confidential,\n                your systems remain operational, and your reputation remains intact.\n            </p>\n            <div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n    