br>\n                Phone: <span style=\"color: #d32f2f;\">+1 (800) 555-SECURE</span>\n            </p>\n            <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;\">\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Request a Quote</a>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 SecureNet Solutions. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}